Mikonos and Orete.

135
01:07:33,783 --> 01:07:34,772
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

136
01:07:34,851 --> 01:07:37,376
I'm so anxious to see all the
beautiful old temples and theaters.

137
01:07:37,454 --> 01:07:38,443
Oh, God.

138
01:07:38,521 --> 01:07:39,954
Yeah. Oh, I'll do that with you.
