She said it was important.

185
01:09:16,820 --> 01:09:18,310
Excuse me.

186
01:09:19,656 --> 01:09:21,647
- Tomorrow morning?
- Do you wanna come?

187
01:09:21,724 --> 01:09:24,420
That bloody phone
has not stopped ringing all weekend.

188
01:09:24,494 --> 01:09:26,519
- I know.
- It's so irritating.

189
01:09:26,963 --> 01:09:27,952
Hello?

190
01:09:28,031 --> 01:09:30,226
