on Samantha too, frankly.

213
01:10:31,127 --> 01:10:32,492
Yeah. Well, it's unfortunate,

214
01:10:32,562 --> 01:10:34,689
but, you know,
Ohris has a lot of responsibility.

215
01:10:34,764 --> 01:10:36,425
