and we'll get it sorted.

230
01:11:03,793 --> 01:11:05,556
- I'm not doing that again.
- Again?

231
01:11:05,628 --> 01:11:08,188
- What's that supposed to mean?
- It's the third time.

232
01:11:08,264 --> 01:11:10,789
I did it once when I was younger,
and then I did it for Tom.

233
01:11:10,867 --> 01:11:12,664
I didn't want to, but he insisted.

234
01:11:12,735 --> 01:11:14,703
Nola, I really can't see any other way.

235
01:11:14,771 --> 01:11:16,762
- Why can't I just have it?
- And what?

236
01:11:16,839 --> 01:11:19,774
- And we'll raise it together.
- That's obviously not possible.

237
01:11:19,842 --> 01:11:21,810
