248
01:11:52,141 --> 01:11:54,268
Us.

249
01:11:54,711 --> 01:11:56,702
Is something wrong?

250
01:11:58,615 --> 01:12:00,913
Yeah. There is.

251
01:12:02,418 --> 01:12:03,407
