Of course I'm not. Don't be silly.

265
01:13:05,848 --> 01:13:08,373
Do you not love me anymore?

266
01:13:10,586 --> 01:13:12,781
Of course I love you.

267
01:13:14,023 --> 01:13:16,150
Well, what's wrong?

268
01:13:19,362 --> 01:13:21,592
I just feel like I'm letting you down.

269
01:13:21,664 --> 01:13:23,689
