270
01:13:26,703 --> 01:13:29,331
Is it because I'm not getting pregnant?

271
01:13:32,642 --> 01:13:34,633
I just...

272
01:13:35,278 --> 01:13:37,678
...feel so guilty.

273
01:13:38,481 --> 01:13:41,211
